BackupPlan_full_interval:
backup plan's full backup interval.
 if full period is DAILY, then the unit of full_interval is day.
 if full period is WEEKLY, then the unit of full_interval is week,
 if full period is MONTHLY, then the unit of full_interval is month.
BackupPlan_full_time_point: backup plan's full backup time point. date? 0-31, date_position 1/-1 weekday? 0-6, hour int, minute int?
BackupPlan_incremental_time_points:
backup plan's incremental backup time point. weekday? 0-6, hour int, minute int
 if weekday is set, it will override the config in incremental_weekdays
BackupPlan_incremental_weekdays: the week days set of incremental, but can be override by incremental time points
BackupPlan_keep_policy: backup plan's restore point keep policy
BackupPlan_keep_policy_value:
backup plan's restore point keep policy value
 if keep policy is TIME, this value is time in days
 if keep policy is COUNT, this value is count
 if keep policy is FOREVER, this value is 0.
